para_trans: For housing projects implemented by Maharashtra Housing Development Corporation (Mahahousing)
By providing funds from the Maharashtra Shelter Fund
Government Correctional Certificate No: Mahahausingh / 2023 / Q. No.146 / Home Fund-2
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Government Decision, Housing Department No. Mahahousing / 2023 / Q. No. 146 / Housing Fund-2, dated 06.09.2024.

Read the last two lines in issue number 5 of the government decision here "Maharashtra Housing Development Corporation (MAHDC) and MHADA are fully responsible for the primary deposit in the Maharashtra Shelter Fund."
Authority will remain. "It said. Instead, "primary deposit in Maharashtra Shelter Fund."
The Maharashtra Housing Development Corporation (MAHDC) will be fully responsible for doing so. Read this.
The Government Corrigendum is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
